  ('optician-moex-01889', 'optician', 'optician-moex-108-72ff33b8', 'sub-optician-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關理想的軟式隱形眼鏡驗配，下列敘述何者正確？', '["注視正前方時完全覆蓋角膜，其他注視方向未覆蓋區小於1 mm", "眨眼時滑動需超過0.5 mm", "邊緣應顯示挑起，才不會壓迫角膜周邊血管", "注視任何方向鏡片應該保持位於角膜中心"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:35+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "93c9062a697c", "answer_pdf_sha1": "3d13dcd1ce1a", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "108110", "c": "113", "s": "1108", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "隱形眼鏡學概要", "year": "108", "exam_name": "108年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試、108年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力...", "original_question_number": 20, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optician", "db_exam_id": "optician"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optician-moex-01890', 'optician', 'optician-moex-108-72ff33b8', 'sub-optician-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '患者配戴的隱形眼鏡參數為基弧= 8.25 mm、直徑（OAD）= 9.8 mm，隱形眼鏡配適情形良好，今將 鏡片直徑改為9.3 mm，若要維持原來相同的配適狀態，則下列基弧何者最正確？', '["基弧= 8.15 mm", "基弧= 8.55 mm", "基弧= 7.95 mm", "基弧= 7.60 mm"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:35+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "93c9062a697c", "answer_pdf_sha1": "3d13dcd1ce1a", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "108110", "c": "113", "s": "1108", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "隱形眼鏡學概要", "year": "108", "exam_name": "108年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試、108年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力...", "original_question_number": 21, "answer_corrected": true, "flags": ["answer_corrected_skip_v1"], "slug": "optician", "db_exam_id": "optician"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optician-moex-01891', 'optician', 'optician-moex-108-72ff33b8', 'sub-optician-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '有患者框架眼鏡處方為-3.50DS/-1.75DC×010，配戴雙邊上下削薄（double slab off）軟式散光隱形眼 鏡試片，經檢查發現試戴片上3點與9點方向的定位線停在2點與8點方位，向廠商訂隱形眼鏡其 最佳處方為？', '["-3.50DS/-1.75DC×l60", "-3.50DS/-1.75DC×150", "-3.50DS/-1.50DC×040", "-3.50DS/-1.50DC×l60"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:35+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "93c9062a697c", "answer_pdf_sha1": "3d13dcd1ce1a", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "108110", "c": "113", "s": "1108", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "隱形眼鏡學概要", "year": "108", "exam_name": "108年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試、108年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力...", "original_question_number": 22, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optician", "db_exam_id": "optician"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optician-moex-01892', 'optician', 'optician-moex-108-72ff33b8', 'sub-optician-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關軟式隱形眼鏡配適過緊，下列敘述何者錯誤？', '["一戴上鏡片就能明顯感到不適", "透過角膜曲率計觀察角膜反射光圈是扭曲模糊，患者眨眼後隨即改善", "相較而言，矽水膠鏡片比水膠鏡片更易觀察到球結膜壓痕", "可更換較大的BOZR來改善"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:35+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "93c9062a697c", "answer_pdf_sha1": "3d13dcd1ce1a", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "108110", "c": "113", "s": "1108", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "隱形眼鏡學概要", "year": "108", "exam_name": "108年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試、108年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力...", "original_question_number": 23, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optician", "db_exam_id": "optician"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optician-moex-01893', 'optician', 'optician-moex-108-72ff33b8', 'sub-optician-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '眼鏡度數-4.50DS/-0.50DC×180，角膜弧度42.00@180/43.50@090，其計算殘餘散光（calculated residual astigmatism）是多少？', '["-1.00×090", "-1.00×180", "-2.00×090", "-2.00×180"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:35+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "93c9062a697c", "answer_pdf_sha1": "3d13dcd1ce1a", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "108110", "c": "113", "s": "1108", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "隱形眼鏡學概要", "year": "108", "exam_name": "108年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試、108年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力...", "original_question_number": 24, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optician", "db_exam_id": "optician"}'::jsonb, NULL),
